node.text: “Mint Chocolate Chip Ice Cream” can #2 of #6 for our next OOO release Saturday 7/31 🎃 6.4% 🎅 Our lactose sour base conditioned on Dark Chocolate Chips, Milk Chocolate Bars, and a very small dosage of Mint. We then blended the batch with loads of Vanilla Ice Cream. Presale this coming Friday 7/23 at 7pm through our web store.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by RAR Brewing in RAR Brewing. May be an image of drink and text that says 'OUT OF PEOPLE EOPLEATER TER CUPCAKES ORDER AMERICAN SOUR PINT 6.4% @ ALCBYVO BREWED BY RAR IN AMBRIDGE, nan'.

node.text: “People Eater Cupcakes” can #1 of #6 for our next OOO release Saturday 7/31 🎃 6.4% 🎅 Our lactose sour base conditioned on Welch’s Grape, Funfetti Cake, Cake Batter, and Vanilla Buttercream Frosting. Presale this coming Friday 7/23 at 7pm through our web store.

node.text: Two new 60bbl fermenters. Step 1 of 3 for more/expanded core products come Fall. Pales, Lagers, 12-PK Boxes, Variety Packs, Year-round Pulp, Seasonal’s, and most importantly AVAILABILITY. Fall/Winter goals along with much much more 🙌🍻
